        ) produces a candidate (i.e. a node in
        VC
        ).
        GT‚Å¢C=(VT‚Å¢C,ET‚Å¢C)
        is an unweighted bipartite graph that ties
        GT
        and
        GC
        together and represents ‚Äúauthorship‚Äù. The graph
